ADDITIONAL NOTICE — Cybersecurity tooling

This repository ships utilities (reverse-shell payload generation, hash
cracking, subdomain enumeration, etc.) intended for authorized testing on
systems the operator owns or has explicit written permission to assess.
Unauthorized use against third-party systems may violate the Computer Fraud
and Abuse Act, the Information Technology Act 2000 (India), the Computer
Misuse Act 1990 (UK), and equivalent laws in your jurisdiction. You are
solely responsible for how you use these tools.
